    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.basics.header": "Horizontal Solar Generator Basics",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.basics.text_1": "The Horizontal Solar Generator produces identical RPM and SU to the vertical one (16 RPM)",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.basics.text_2": "The Advanced Horizontal Solar Generator produces identical RPM and SU to the vertical one (32 RPM)",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.basics.text_3": "Both require direct access to the sky",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.header": "Directional Generation",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_1": "Horizontal Solar Generators calculate SU dynamically based on facing direction and time of day",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_2": "These range from 128 to 1024 SU for the Standard",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_3": "And 256 to 2048 SU for the Advanced",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_4": "East facing generators reach maximum efficiency in the morning",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_5": "West facing generators reach maximum efficiency in the evening",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_6": "North and South facing generators produce a constant reduced output",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.directions.text_7": "Standard: 128 SU, Advanced: 256 SU",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.dyeing.header": "Color Variants",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.dyeing.text_1": "Both Standard and Advanced Horizontal Solar Generators can be dyed",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.dyeing.text_2": "Right-click with any dye to change the color",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.dyeing.text_3": "You can also craft them with dyes",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.header": "Obstructions",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_1": "The generator checks up to 10 blocks in front of its solar face for blocks",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_2": "If no block is in its way it produces its full efficiency",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_3": "Transparent blocks don't affect the production",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_4": "If you place a solid block directly in front of it, the generator produces 0",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_5": "If you have a solid block from the 2nd to 10th position",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_6": "The generator is considered 'shadowed' and it produces its bare minimum",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.horizontal_solar_generator.obstructions.text_7": "128 SU for the standard and 256 SU for the advanced",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.header": "Solar Generator Basics",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_1": "The Solar Generator creates rotational force from sunlight",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_2": "Connect shafts to transfer the rotation",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_3": "The generator must have direct access to the sky",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_4": "It generates 16 RPM with 16 SU capacity",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_5": "Use a Wrench while sneaking to reverse the rotation direction",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_basics.text_6": "The rotation will now spin in the opposite direction",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_dyeing.header": "Color Variants",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_dyeing.text_1": "Solar Generators come in 17 color variants",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_dyeing.text_2": "Right-click with any dye to change the color",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_dyeing.text_3": "Or craft any generator with a dye in a crafting table",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_dyeing.text_4": "All color variants function identically",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_obstructions.header": "Obstructions",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_obstructions.text_1": "The Solar Generator requires direct sky access",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_obstructions.text_2": "Solid blocks completely obstruct sky access - No power!",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_obstructions.text_3": "Glass allows light through - power!",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_obstructions.text_4": "Snow layers and carpets also block the generator",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_weather.header": "Weather Effects",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_weather.text_1": "During clear weather, the generator runs at full speed (16 RPM)",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_weather.text_2": "During rain, power is reduced to half (8 RPM)",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_weather.text_3": "During thunderstorms, the generator stops completely",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_generator_weather.text_4": "At night, there is not enough light to generate power",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.header": "Advanced Solar Windmills",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_1": "The Solar Windmill Bearing supports all sail blocks",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_2": "You can mix all kinds of sails",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_3": "The SU production of the Solar Sails and the Default Sails will be combined",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_4": "Resulting, in this scenario, in 1536 SU",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_5": "During the day, the production of Solar Sails is double that of Default Sails",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_6": "When raining it is 50%% more than the Solar Sails",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.advanced.text_7": "When night and thunder, the Solar Sails produce as much as the Default Sails",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.header": "Assembling Solar Windmills",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.text_1": "Solar Sails are handy blocks to create Solar Windmills with",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.text_2": "They will attach to blocks and each other without the need of Super Glue",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.text_3": "Right-Click with Dye to paint them",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.text_4": "The solar sails produce double the amount of power as a regular solar generator",
    "createphotomovement.ponder.solar_sail.basics.text_5": "8 solar sails produce 1024 SU while the default sails produce 512 SU",
    "itemGroup.createphotomovement": "Create Photomovement"
}